Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把衣服收進來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之快點給我收進來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  阪本先生  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雨下得真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服有幫我收進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為阪本要我收進去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦  真的是阪本說要我收進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為阪本先生說要收進去  然後衣服就掉下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦  阪本先生說收進去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後說把衣服弄掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嚇死我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎說什麼啊  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是那樣說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有說「把衣服弄掉下來」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有說！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  就把阪本當做祭品來補償吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦  衣服髒了洗一下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天這樣的已經無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚飯你們倆都不准吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  為什麼要牽連我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是這是阪本犯的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把阪本當做祭品來補償就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那麼我就收下阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只不准博士吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦  那麼就讓博士來當祭品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為把衣服弄掉的是博士  把衣服弄得濕濕的也是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘  今天的晚飯是蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雞蛋很便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  博士今天不是不能吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…算了  總之今天就讓你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了  太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就不准你吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水  水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚鯊魚  啪哢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚鯊魚  啪庫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘土自塑像的作業你們不覺得超麻煩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  那個作業今天要交嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧  美緒老師  莫非您忘記了喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為是明天交啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣你做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連麻衣都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子要下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是下雨能形容的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要天變地異了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天變地異…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:16.36,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,300)\fad(400,00)}日\N常\N之\N81
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對我的寺廟做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些香火錢小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}希望世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘟神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我的寺廟裡滾出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走下去吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們這樣想著  任憑晚秋的雨打在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:15.89,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(400,00)}日\N常\N之\N82
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我要和高崎老師決勝  能請您來當裁判嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指圍棋足球的裁判嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  如果我獲勝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師會二話不說來當顧問的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能成功的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我之前借你的「圍棋足球入門」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看過那個就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒看入門書是我的不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這兩人從剛才開始在做什麼  我完全搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是圍棋足球！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你看了入門書也不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人可謂是一開始就使出了禁招的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是理論上的至高等級攻防
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如那筆直的手  如果把那比作圍棋盤的腿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手的那個架勢就是棋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍一看他倆很和諧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從他腳上夾著的球來看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的推測  他們兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為太陽的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼我完全不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be Loved
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木  那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兩人之間流動著緊繃的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是亂來的話   會有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是很久沒有看到這樣高等級的比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得連風都變得躁動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  這個姿勢是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在非正式比賽中使出那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這狀況  可不能放著不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  請允許我使出那招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了正義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為放射光芒的星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木禁招流超奧義之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是  「Ahh Final loved」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我以輕鬆的心情創造的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又變成了不得了的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
